# AI Serial Debug Tool

> A next-generation serial port debugger built with Electron, combining an AI-powered assistant, TCP/UDP forwarding, protocol frame parsing, and more — all wrapped in the Lightcore Prism design language with dark/light themes and Chinese/English localization.

[![License: GPL-3.0](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-GPL--3.0-blue.svg)](https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0)
[![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-Windows-lightgrey.svg)](https://github.com/)
[![Electron](https://img.shields.io/badge/Electron-28-47848F.svg)](https://www.electronjs.org/)
[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-1.0.0-green.svg)](https://github.com/)

