## Features

### Serial Communication
- Auto-detect and list all available serial port devices
- Baud rates 300 ~ 2,000,000 · Data bits 5/6/7/8 · Stop bits 1/1.5/2 · Parity None/Even/Odd/Mark/Space
- Real-time connection status, clean one-click connect/disconnect

### Data Display
- Text / HEX dual-mode display, switchable at any time
- Per-line timestamps in `[HH:MM:SS.mmm]` format
- Color-coded RX / TX lines; errors highlighted prominently
- Auto-scroll with pause option and one-click clear
- Live save of received data to file

### Data Sending
- Text or HEX send mode; optional CR / LF / CR+LF appended automatically
- Timed send: set interval (ms) and repeat count, runs automatically
- `Ctrl+Enter` shortcut to send instantly

### Multi-Command Group
- Add any number of send commands, each with its own delay (ms)
- Sequential send, loop send
- Configuration persisted across restarts

### Protocol Frame Parser
- Custom frame header, footer, and length-field offset / byte count
- Automatically extracts complete frames from the receive buffer and highlights them
- Works in HEX mode

### TCP/UDP Forwarding
- **TCP Server**: listen on a port, accept multiple clients, transparent bidirectional relay
- **TCP Client**: connect to a remote server, transparent bidirectional relay
- **UDP**: bind a local port, bidirectional forward to a configured remote host:port
- Live forwarding status display

### AI Assistant
- Embedded AI chat panel with **Agent mode**
- Agent mode ships 15 serial-port tools: read/write port, scan ports, send command groups, parse protocol frames, and more
- Works with any OpenAI-compatible API — local (Ollama, LM Studio) or cloud (ChatGPT, DeepSeek, etc.)
- MCP (Model Context Protocol) tool-call extension support
- Full tool-call trace visible in the chat

### UI & Experience
- Lightcore Prism design: glass morphism surfaces, prism gradient borders, animated orb backgrounds
- Dark / Light theme toggle, preference persisted
- Chinese / English UI toggle, preference persisted
- Frameless custom title bar; always-on-top toggle
- Built-in offline user manual
- Quick link to buy hardware accessories

